@startuml
title Onboarding 3-Step First Success Plan

actor User
participant OW as "Onboarding Wizard"
participant REC as "Recommendation Engine"
participant WS as "Workspace Connect"
participant PM as "PM Intake"
participant UI as "First Success Surface"

User -> OW: Step 1\nTell us what you are building
OW -> REC: compute recommendations
REC --> OW: blueprint + runtime + starter request

User -> OW: Accept recommended path
OW -> WS: Step 2\nConnect repo
WS -> WS: detect project/workspace
WS -> WS: run environment check
WS --> OW: ready / needs attention / blocked

User -> OW: Step 3\nLaunch first request
OW -> PM: create onboarding issue
PM --> UI: onboardingIssueId

UI -> UI: Show issue detail welcome banner
UI -> UI: Show setup checklist
UI -> UI: Guide clarification / first success

@enduml
